'''Benen''' ko [[leydi]] e [[Afirik]]. Laamorde (kapital) leydi Benen yo Porto Novo. Mbertudi leydi ndin ko 114.763 km2, jamaa hoɗuɗo e mayri no hewtaynoo fewndo hitaande 2016 yimɓe 10,872,298.

== Sufoore ==
Benen ɗun lesdi famardi eder cirol lesɗe geɓe [[Afirik|Afirika]] gonde hirna. Yimɓe lesdiɗin eɓe bolwira wolde Faransakore e jangirki ɗemgal maɓɓe ɓen wada yadu noɓe kutirta e galu lamu maɓɓe. Benin hauti kerol e lesɗe ha nayi hanje goni [[Naajeeriya]] ta funa mari ta hirna bo Togo ta woilamabo kautal [[Niiser]] e ta wuttudu woilaru ko yari hirna bo ɗi henɗi kerol e [[Burkina Faso]]. Jengal [[Faransi]] hangal woni wolde lesdi Benen. Lesdi ɗin eɗi woɗi ɗuɗirka yimbe tamami 4, 418,000 e dungu 1988.

Gelle mauɗe mari kanje goni Kotono mangu majun yari jajirka kilomita 114,763. Benen un lesɗi goduɗi e diskuɗi lesdi e demal kadima e ta teure hottollo ɗen e nebban boɗejam ɗan lio (palm oil) e ta ɗer marilawo gol lesdi ɗin ɗarori e hora mari e dardi a tal mangal hebgo nattugo hanjunke demal geɓe lesdi Benin. 

